FizzBuzz: Print numbers 1–100, 'Fizz' for multiples of 3, 'Buzz' for 5, 'FizzBuzz' for both

for i in range(1,101):
    if (i%3==0 and i%5!=0):
        print(i,'-->fizzbuzz')
    elif(i%3==0):
        print(i,'-->fizz')
    elif(i%5==0):
        print(i,'-->buzz')
    else:
        print(i)

Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(1)
